Author: lyssland
Text: thank you!!! i needed to hear this. i did have to push back an hour but i will be okay and you're right 💕💕💕

Author: throwawayedfeelz
Text: Hey this is late and I'm sorry, but I understand how hard IF windows getting messed with feels. I find it helps to know that our bodies aren't as clockwork as people like to think - they don't measure time so meticulously. I promise it's not the end of the world, you can get back on track ❤️❤️
